/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f564cfaee330318e105477bb39a62af1a94f0bd9","tid":848530,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T09:54:08.000Z","msg":"都無咩新料嘅<br />\n全部近排有上開連登政事台嘅都會知"},{"pid":"1dfac8fee2ec4fd8a6f475cca7985bd3cde92749","tid":848530,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T10:09:01.000Z","msg":"上埋hkgpao <br />\n<br />\n《文匯報》起底 理大學渣<br />\n原來是學獨聯爪牙<br />\n<br />\n昨日理工大學發生浸大佔領的翻版，一班理大學渣公然「禁錮」師長，甚至令師長仆倒跪地，場面惡劣，學渣可恥（按此重溫相關報道）！當中一名自稱關姓學生的四眼仔，在「禁錮」師長時情緒激動，更不斷枱櫈及大聲叫囂，事後經《文匯報》起底後，其自稱關姓的四眼仔原來為「港獨」組織「學生獨立聯盟」爪牙，真實姓名為何俊謙，而且更獨到出汗，不時上街播獨！<br />\n<br />\n據《文匯報》報道指出，今年30歲的何俊謙不是學生會幹事會成員，目前在理大入讀碩士課程，更曾經以網名「關愛座Hunter」在各大討論區挑機他人，據知情人士向《文匯報》透露，何俊謙曾經於網上惹火頭，更於不同討論區中發表仇視國家及香港政府的言論，而且更講到明撐港獨。<br />\n<br />\n經網民起底後獨得高調<br />\n何俊謙是於今年三月才正式獲召集人陳家駒邀請加入「學生獨立聯盟」，其後每次播獨事件都可見何俊謙蹤影，更不時帶頭搞事！據知何俊謙起初播獨時都會遮遮掩掩，像是今年5月底在「聲援」梁天琦活動時，會刻意避被拍上鏡上鏡，但因事後在網上被網民起底後，才變得高調。何俊謙於七一遊行時開始變得高調，甚至與陳家駒帶頭叫囂。而何俊謙於8月底時，更高調到獨自到灣仔入境處大樓「爭取子女居留權家長協會」的示威中搞亂，獨得愈來愈明顯，更愈來愈想出位！<br />\n<br />\n何俊謙在外獨得出晒面，明顯是想出位，但在「禁錮」師長卻假扮關姓學生？似乎又好似淆底囉！獨友搞事，絕不輕饒，理大校方必須嚴懲搞事學生！<br />\n<br />\n原圖：文匯報、學生獨立聯盟Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkgpao.com/articles/228994\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkgpao.com%2Farticles%2F228994&d=%2FrE3f8HXw7%2BNXC4UwzoGVtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=012ce15d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkgpao.com/articles/228994</a>"},{"pid":"78e4533841dfa592280af5d3690a8739b2814b1a","tid":848530,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37bd37dda97f9db4c0275f693d6645dd4112d9ab","tid":848530,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63a7e099ab7364e853e272042b174fcdd65b6460","tid":848530,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa45f7e916047d42f4aaef83379550cc13449339","tid":848530,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T09:44:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T09:53:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T10:11:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d753a2bd4261230f9f2cd1e36d77e3e0c0aaeee1","tid":848530,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T10:14:52.000Z","msg":"理大「獨」生邏輯 真係識條鐵<br />\n<br />\n理工大學再有「獨」生圍堵辱罵老師，自稱不屬學生會的「關姓」學生，實情係「港獨」組織「學生獨立聯盟」骨幹、網名「關愛座Hunter」嘅何俊謙，就跟埋班學生會成員到大學高層辦公室「洗樓」鬧事，佢不斷高聲咆哮，又挑釁保安，大叫「唔好同我哋講秩序！」、「無辦法，你咁唔好彩係度打工，我就連你一齊鬧！」究竟乜嘢邏輯？大聲夾惡就大晒？你估而家拍緊《古惑仔》，你係揸Fit人咩！<br />\n<br />\n根據「關姓」學生嘅邏輯，係咪「無辦法，你咁唔好彩係女人，我就要強姦你！」又或者「無辦法，你咁有錢又畀我見到，我就要老笠你！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dotdotnews.com/2018/10/05/picture/理大「獨」生邏輯-真係識條鐵\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dotdotnews.com%2F2018%2F10%2F05%2Fpicture%2F%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E3%80%8C%E7%8D%A8%E3%80%8D%E7%94%9F%E9%82%8F%E8%BC%AF-%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E8%AD%98%E6%A2%9D%E9%90%B5&d=%2FrE3f8HXw7%2BNXC4UwzoGVtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=a70420b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dotdotnews.com/2018/10/05/picture/理大「獨」生邏輯-真係識條鐵</a>"},{"pid":"e8c1e1213ae564c7e7ee5ab7ea7d32cbd1ee6060","tid":848530,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d72f58b5edbafd8ea72f628c36161fe2efffed01","tid":848530,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T07:08:05.000Z","msg":"九成係你啦漿囝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T10:14:59.000Z","msg":"一定係記者上連登照copy蔣仔堆post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7eda1094b76fce758a525d4c416112c6b0436a","tid":848530,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1f880249fcbaacfbcd8e6357fe048ea63f7872f3","tid":848530,"uid":2436,"like":11,"dislike":12,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T06:46:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T10:19:15.000Z","msg":"你唔係好support劉細良咩？咁你嘈咩啫"},{"pid":"c766d68ee086b347de21777c72fdeb971c5d85c6","tid":848530,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T10:20:02.000Z","m